oks-amazing-and-completely-bananas-fans-react-to-bonkers-robbie-williams-biopic-better-man-trailer-3799045">“这看起来棒极了，而且完全是香蕉”：粉丝们对“疯狂”的罗比·威廉姆斯传记片《更好的人》预告片的反应</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Ela Minus 分享欢快的《BROKEN》并宣布新专辑《DIA》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/ela-minus-shares-the-euphoric-broken-and-announces-new-album-dia-3799030?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=ela-minus-shares-欣快破碎并宣布新专辑迪亚Anagricel DuranWed, 02 Oct 2024 15:30:05 +0000 Music NewsNewsElectronicLive Music News https://www.nme.com/?p=3799030 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ela-Minus.-Credit-Alvaro-Ariso.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="埃拉减号。图片来源：阿尔瓦罗·阿里索" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ela-Minus.-Credit-Alvaro-Ariso.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ela-Minus.-Credit-Alvaro-Ariso-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ela-Minus.-Credit-Alvaro-Ariso-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ela-Minus.-Credit-Alvaro-Ariso-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ela-Minus.-Credit-Alvaro-Ariso-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ela-Minus.-Credit-Alvaro-Ariso-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>她即将推出的专辑继 2020 年的《Acts of Rebellion》之后</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ela-minus-shares-the-euphoric-broken-and-announces-new-album-dia-3799030">Ela Minus 分享了欢快的《BROKEN》，并宣布新专辑《DIA》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ela-Minus.-Credit-Alvaro-Ariso.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="埃拉减号。图片来源：阿尔瓦罗·阿里索" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ela-Minus.-Credit-Alvaro-Ariso.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ela-Minus.-Credit-Alvaro-Ariso-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ela-Minus.-Credit-Alvaro-Ariso-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ela-Minus.-Credit-Alvaro-Ariso-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ela-Minus.-Credit-Alvaro-Ariso-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ela-Minus.-Credit-Alvaro-Ariso-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Ela-Minus">Ela Minus</a>分享了她的新单曲《BROKEN》，并宣布即将推出专辑《DIA》。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/ela-minus-acts-of-rebellion-review-radar-2792421">Ela Minus – “Acts of Rebellion”评论：带有 DIY 朋克精神的抗议科技</a></strong></li></ul><p>《BROKEN》以大气合成器开场，在副歌部分发展为欢快的电子舞曲。 <em>“我一直是个傻瓜/表现得很酷/现在我崩溃了”</em> ，减号唱道。</p><p>在新闻稿中谈到这首歌时，这位音乐家分享道：“我开始写这首曲子时以为我很好，但写完时我知道我的情况并非如此。”这首歌的随附视频由 Minus 和 Losmose 联合执导，其中 Minus 穿着灰色长裙和配套套头衫，站在白色房间中央的巨大屏幕前。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Ela Minus - 破碎（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/cF4kF48inMA?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 《BROKEN》是她即将发行的第二张专辑《DIA》中继最近发行的主打单曲《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ela-minus-returns-with-blissed-out-new-single-combat-3762985">COMBAT</a> 》之后发行的第二首单曲。</p><p>根据一份新闻稿，这位音乐家的第二张唱片有望成为“电子音乐领域的一项罕见壮举，其中尖端的制作和震撼空间的声音与新兴歌手兼作曲家真正的自我反思和个人思考相结合。”</p><p> 《DIA》被描述为“既内省又广阔，其广泛的歌曲比以往任何时候都更多地揭示了埃拉作为个人和制作人的一面。”该唱片定于 1 月 17 日通过 Domino 发行，并可<a href="https://elaminus.ffm.to/dia" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订/预保存</a>。</p><p> “‘ABRIR MONTE’是我家乡常用的一个短语，指的是在茂密的树叶中开辟道路的行为。我一直很喜欢它的诗意。这就是制作这张唱片的感觉，向内和向外开辟新的道路，继续深入探索未知的领域，”米努斯解释道。 </p><figure id="attachment_3799049" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3799049" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3799049" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ela-Minus-DIA-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="Ela Minus &#39;DIA&#39; 专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ela-Minus-DIA-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ela-Minus-DIA-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ela-Minus-DIA-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ela-Minus-DIA-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ela-Minus-DIA-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ela-Minus-DIA-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ela-Minus-DIA-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3799049" class="wp-caption-text"> Ela Minus &#39;DIA&#39; 专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><h2><strong>“DIA”曲目列表是：</strong></h2><p> <strong>1.“阿布里尔·蒙特”</strong><br /> <strong>2.“破碎”</strong><br /> <strong>3.“偶像”</strong><br /> <strong>4.“我不知道”</strong><br /> <strong>5.“QQ”</strong><br /> <strong>6.“我想变得更好”</strong><br /> <strong>7.“继续”</strong><br /> <strong>8.“与”</strong><br /> <strong>9.“向上”</strong><br /> <strong>10.“战斗”</strong></p><p>为了支持“DIA”，Ela 将参加<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/caribou">Caribou</a>的 2025 年欧盟/英国巡演，并将在标志性的 Melkweg 场地举行的年度 ADE 阿姆斯特丹舞蹈活动上支持<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/floating-points">Floating Points</a> 。查看下面的完整旅游日期列表并<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fela-minus-tickets%2Fartist%2F5230687" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处购买门票</a>。</p><h2> <strong>Ela Minus 2024/2025 直播日期为：</strong></h2><p><strong>十月</strong><br /><strong>16 – 荷兰阿姆斯特丹，梅尔克韦格 (ADE) ^</strong><br /> <strong>19 – 法国巴黎，From Our Minds / FVTVR（巴塞尔艺术展） – DJ set</strong></p><p><strong>十二月</strong><br /><strong>14 – 柏林